    <small><font face="Verdana"><strong>Add New Info Here</strong></font></small>
    </a>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td valign="top" align="left">
		<font face="verdana" size="2">
		<b>Description:</b> <br>
		This spell is the upgrade from summon water. The spell will make four water items at a time.<BR>
<BR>
<B>Research:</B><BR>Words of Transcendence, Water Flask, Summon Drink Scroll
		</font>
	 </td>
	 <td rowspan="4" valign="top" align="right">
    
