			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Everfount isn't that hard to make, You need:<BR>
1 Falsk water......(non summoned)<BR>
1 summon water spell<BR>
1 Words of Transendence<BR>
1 Elemental Grimoir......(book sorta like a sewing kit)<BR>
<BR>
Put all the above into the Elemental Book and combine.  Of course you will fail a few so buy extras, it only took me 2 tries to make it and all I did was put 28 points into Reaserch.The only thing hard to find are the Words of Trans.  I got them off a vendoer in HighPass Hold.  In fact I bought 2 off a vendor and got another buy AUCTIONING in that zone.  The words drop off of the goblins in highpass.  The vendors will only have it if a player has sold it to them.  So be prepared to be there a few night before you actually get the Words.  I love it and think it was worth the extra time, 20 water one crack sure beats summoning over and over and over.
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
