	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				If anyone finds Everfount at a vendor, it's been sold to that vendor by a player.<BR>
<BR>
Cornucopia is for sale in the Herb Jar, next to the Mage guild in Qeynos.  Everfont must be researched, or purchased from a player who researched it.  They will always summon 20 water or bread, even when you are level 24.  If you get Words of Transcendence, a flask of non-summoned water, and the level 1 spell scroll Summon Water, you can attempt to make Everfont in your Grimoir.<BR>
<BR>
And you don't HAVE to purchase either one... If you use Words of Transcendence, a loaf of non-summoned bread, and the level 1 spell scroll Summon Food you can attempt to make Cornucopia in your Grimoir.<BR>
<BR>
Loraff 49 Mage<BR>
<BR>

