	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				The above poster is wrong when you get research at level 16 your max skill in research is not 80. this is because research skill max is calculated differently than most skills - it is (level-15)*5.This means that at level 16 your max skill is 5. However you learn the skill at level 16 (above your max!) but that is why you cannot allocate any more points to it. the next time you can allocate it is when you reach level 19, because 19-15=4, and then 4*5=20. So you can then allocate four more points to raise it from 16 to 20. You can then raise it 5 more per level gained from then on.  Alos regarding a WAY previous post I am certain I saw EverFount and Cornucopia at the library in Erudin. Can't remember if it was in the lower portion of the merchants inventory or in the upper &quot;constant&quot; area.
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
